channel.title: Server not getting online
channel.description:
Hello peepz, I made an own private server, But it's not getting online. Look here is the problem: I start up my NO-IP DUC and compile.bat; and then i start up moparscape and if i ping/using new server, it says my server is not online And if i put on Runserver.bat too it says: Error: Unable to startup listener on 43594 - port already in use? What's problem? Please help me :) :(
Best regards -- Ii Owned Uu
